Wikipedia editors (Konstable, SharkD, and Jacobolus in particular) - documentation of color models and formulas
Eugene Vishnevsky and Nan C. Schaller - "Introduction to Color", which first taught me the virtues and methods of HSV
Vladlen Koltun - miscellaneous texture source images
